1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 8=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:36,470
You talk too much. Shut up.

4
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:40,670
This is hollow.

5
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:42,660
Why did the lights go out?

6
00:00:42,926 --> 00:00:44,135
The ghost blew out the candle?

7
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,070
The ghost are here.

8
00:00:45,070 --> 00:00:45,910
Where's the big face?

9
00:01:02,350 --> 00:01:03,430
You owe me another life.

10
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:06,000
Thanks, Ms. He.

11
00:01:11,230 --> 00:01:13,200
This seems to be a place
for offering statues.

12
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,230
Doesn't this look like Guanyin?

13
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:20,790
And this one looks like the Buddha.

14
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,560
Then this must be Tang Sanzang.

15
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,790
There seems to be a Sha Wujing up ahead.

16
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:28,640
Where's Sun Wukong?

17
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,280
I don't know where he is.

18
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,040
But Zhu Bajie

19
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:34,150
is right beside me.

20
00:01:35,430 --> 00:01:36,480
Come on, dear.

21
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,560
I'll carry you.

22
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,430
This is not Gao Village.

23
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,510
This seems to be a Tang tomb.

24
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,600
Why?

25
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:47,590
Tang Sancai.

26
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:51,560
It was often used as a burial object
in the Tang dynasty.

27
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,590
This room has six corners.

28
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,950
In Feng Shui,
corners mean evil influences.

29
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:01,680
Why are there
so many Buddha statues here?

30
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,000
Isn't that a good thing?

31
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:10,800
Empty.

32
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:12,910
Take it apart.

33
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,560
Come on. One, two, three.

34
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,080
Give it to me.

35
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:30,840
There's something inside.

36
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,560
It's really deep.

37
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,870
I can't see the bottom.

38
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:05,190
What kind of place is this?

39
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,870
What's worshipped here aren't gods.

40
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:29,550
It's people.

41
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,430
That big face was just here.

42
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,430
How did it disappear?

43
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:33,280
What's there to fear?

44
00:03:33,290 --> 00:03:35,056
Who here hasn't gotten blood
on their hands?

45
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:36,310
Have you ever seen a ghost?

46
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,470
Light the lamp.

47
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,360
It's back.

48
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,630
It came out again.

49
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:04,360
I get it now.

50
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:06,840
It's an optical illusion.

51
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,030
What illusion?

52
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,150
When we first came in,

53
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,103
there was nothing here.

54
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:11,400
After we lit the lamp,

55
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:12,710
this face appeared.

56
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,356
It's caused by changes in light

57
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,720
and the viewing angle.

58
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,040
That's not right.

59
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,310
Just now,

60
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,390
when the face wasn't there,

61
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,800
those two jade pieces were still there.

62
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,360
How about this?

63
00:04:27,646 --> 00:04:28,785
Let's put the lamp out again.

64
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,800
Let's take another look.

65
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:31,910
Put out the lamp.

66
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:42,710
Still there.

67
00:04:42,730 --> 00:04:43,570
Look.

68
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,440
Yeah.

69
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:48,160
The tomb builder

70
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,480
must have created this illusion

71
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,270
to guard against tomb raiders.

72
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,830
So, after all that,

73
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:55,000
it's just a trick to scare people.

74
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,013
Don't block me. I want to look at it.

75
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,680
Let me tell you.

76
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,680
Those two jade pieces being here

77
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:04,190
must have a reason.

78
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:06,830
It might even be a mechanism.

79
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,640
Hi, Miss Bai.

80
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,623
I think you're a decent person.

81
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,390
Let me teach you something.

82
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,830
See those holes up there?

83
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,390
Know what they're for?

84
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,630
They're called quicksand holes.

85
00:05:24,317 --> 00:05:26,016
If the mechanism
is triggered incorrectly,

86
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,190
sand will pour out.

87
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:30,070
What about those ones?

88
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:31,720
The same.

89
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,230
All of them

90
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,320
are quicksand holes.

91
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,029
If they all release at once,

92
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,870
we'll be buried in minutes.

93
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:39,770
Let me tell you.

94
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,160
If the sand reaches here,

95
00:05:41,270 --> 00:05:42,680
you won't be able to breathe at all.

96
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,630
It's miserable.

97
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,700
Then what should we do?

98
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,430
Kiss me, and I'll tell you.

99
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,040
Are you serious?

100
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,920
You're moving way too fast.

101
00:05:58,310 --> 00:06:00,720
Don't tell me you're still a virgin.

102
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:03,800
Who are you calling that?

103
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:07,310
I've done it a lot of times.

104
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,630
I was joking.

105
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:09,630
What do we do now?

106
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:11,270
Then I...

107
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,760
Let me tell you.

108
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,600
These jade pieces
should be the mechanism.

109
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:19,750
It has patterns on it.

110
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,680
Line up the patterns,

111
00:06:21,709 --> 00:06:23,765
and the mechanism should open.
Then we can get out.

112
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:24,670
Are you sure?

113
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,870
Archeology experts

114
00:06:26,881 --> 00:06:27,941
are divided into two types.

115
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,190
One kind is like Chen Youxi,

116
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,720
naturally gifted.

117
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,510
The other kind is like me,

118
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,040
experienced and handsome.

119
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:39,310
But you'll need to help me.

120
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,640
How?

121
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,400
Dead end.

122
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,830
Who is this?

123
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,830
The coffin board
is an ordinary material.

124
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,070
Definitely not a noble.

125
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,510
Wearing rough cloth.

126
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:06,510
The skull is blackened.

127
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,240
Probably poisoned to death.

128
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:11,040
Could it be a tomb builder?

129
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:12,600
Possible.

130
00:07:12,993 --> 00:07:15,653
In ancient times, tomb builders
were sometimes buried in the tomb.

131
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,310
Let's check over there.

132
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,080
Miss Bai,

133
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,560
nice moves.

134
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:32,000
Be careful.

135
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,310
I'm guessing that's the mechanism.

136
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,560
Listen to my command.

137
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,480
Rotate 180° clockwise.

138
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,760
Come on.

139
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,480
One, two, three.

140
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,750
How is it? Still blocked?

141
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,590
Still blocked.

142
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,120
Now, we can confirm
these burial companions

143
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,040
were the tomb builders.

144
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,870
Making so many builders
die in the tomb

145
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,040
is really cruel.

146
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,030
Yeah.

147
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,806
That was to prevent the burial treasures

148
00:08:31,870 --> 00:08:33,600
and the secrets of the tomb

149
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:35,200
from leaking out.

150
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,670
Aside from imperial tombs,

151
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,720
what other tomb
would need such a grand setup?

152
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:43,960
Even if they were buried with it,

153
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,809
someone still had to place them

154
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:46,720
inside these walls.

155
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,800
I know now.

156
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,750
The passage we came through earlier

157
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,270
must have been for them to leave.

158
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,160
Look.

159
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,390
What's that?

160
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,550
Let's go check it out.

161
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:01,470
Alright.

162
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,160
Be careful.

163
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,630
Miss Bai, slow down.

164
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,150
Come on. Watch your head.

165
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,280
Alright.

166
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,680
Not bad.

167
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,240
Even without Chen Youxi,

168
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:35,870
you're not completely useless.

169
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,480
Can you speak Chinese?

170
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,720
She's praising you.

171
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:43,670
She's praising you
for not being totally useless.

172
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,200
Of course.

173
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,579
She didn't even bother asking.

174
00:09:46,630 --> 00:09:47,840
In our line of work,

175
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,630
who is better than me?

176
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,000
What about Chen Youxi?

177
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,573
Can we talk about something happy?

178
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,150
We've gone through so many floors.

179
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,600
Everywhere there are Buddha offerings.

180
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,270
So why is there

181
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,720
a Heaven-Earth Shrine here?

182
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:13,150
There must be something behind it.

183
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,326
The Dispelling Umbrella.

184
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,320
Be careful.

185
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,840
Why would there be human statues
inside the shrine?

186
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:50,630
Who would the tomb builders worship?

187
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,360
Forget it.

188
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,393
Let's move it aside first.

189
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:54,470
Alright.

190
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,200
In the middle of nowhere,

191
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,720
this huge Buddha suddenly appears.

192
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:14,670
That's really eerie.

193
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,360
Not bad, right?

194
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:25,110
Blow it up.

195
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,270
The rock stability

196
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:29,080
and structural strength are unknown.

197
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,750
Blasting rashly could cause a collapse.

198
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,200
You finally used your brain.

199
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,440
You think everyone's like you?

200
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:38,836
If you were like me,
you'd already be successful.

201
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,110
Chubby.

202
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,670
You have ten minutes.

203
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,480
Find the mechanism here.

204
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,120
Miss Bai,

205
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,320
you don't understand our line of work.

206
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,790
Our work is clearly divided.

207
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:50,450
For example.

208
00:11:50,461 --> 00:11:51,502
- Here.
- I handle danger.

209
00:11:51,513 --> 00:11:52,476
Help me press the watch.

210
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,270
Chen Youxi is responsible
for the mechanisms.

211
00:11:55,543 --> 00:11:56,630
You can't ask me to do this.

212
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:58,080
If you can't find it in ten minutes,

213
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,720
I'll shoot him.

214
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:03,000
Of course, in special situations,

215
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,200
our divisions aren't that strict.

216
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:12,600
Why can't I be the one
finding the mechanism?

217
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,790
You can shoot him.

218
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:46,176
This one connects through.

219
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:15,960
Two minutes left.

220
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,246
Why haven't you found it yet?

221
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,960
Do you think that when I work,

222
00:13:26,109 --> 00:13:27,202
I shine with my own light?

223
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:30,630
Come on. Walk arm in arm with me.

224
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,150
Our two-person world begins now.

225
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,750
Young lady.

226
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:42,320
I got happy too soon.

227
00:13:58,790 --> 00:13:59,750
You're serious?

228
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:00,989
Huang Long, what are you doing?

229
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,030
Thirty seconds.

230
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,270
Stop rushing me.

231
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,480
I'm looking for it.

232
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,510
Bro,

233
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:07,080
there are still 30 seconds.

234
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,550
Why shoot?

235
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,720
Don't you just want some antiques?

236
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,910
I have a shop outside.

237
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,390
I'll get them for you.

238
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:19,390
If you raid tombs,
you'll get a few years at most.

239
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:21,630
But if you shoot me dead,

240
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:22,770
that's the death penalty.

241
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,800
Ten.

242
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:25,720
Wait.

243
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:27,360
- Nine.
- That won't change anything.

244
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,320
Eight.

245
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,790
- Give me more time.
- Seven.

246
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:31,080
Chubby, hurry up.

247
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,670
- Six.
- Where is it?

248
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:33,990
Five.

249
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:35,510
- The hand.
- Four.

250
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,510
Pull that hand.

251
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:38,510
- Three.
- Chubby, save me.

252
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:39,560
Two.

253
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:40,920
One.

254
00:14:47,610 --> 00:14:50,710
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

255
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:56,070
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

256
00:14:57,130 --> 00:15:01,710
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

257
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:08,860
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

258
00:15:09,420 --> 00:15:20,440
♪La la♪

259
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:29,180
♪No line divides the border♪

260
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:31,960
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

261
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:34,330
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

262
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:37,020
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

263
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:40,230
♪Hey hey hey♪

264
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:43,380
♪Hey hey hey♪

265
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:47,030
♪Hey hey♪

266
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:48,180
♪Hey hey♪

267
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:50,720
♪Hey hey♪

268
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:56,550
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

269
00:15:57,140 --> 00:16:00,850
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

270
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:05,350
♪No difference between you and me♪

271
00:16:05,630 --> 00:16:07,960
♪No lead or side role on this stage♪

272
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:10,170
♪A perfect life is something we share♪

273
00:16:10,390 --> 00:16:12,670
♪Love declares across the sky and earth♪

274
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:18,390
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

275
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:23,240
♪Time and space go beyond all bounds♪

276
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:28,090
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

277
00:16:28,090 --> 00:16:30,180
♪This is our world♪

278
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:35,210
♪Shining lives bring the change♪

279
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:42,300
♪In a blink, to forever♪
